== Overview ==
The ComWave Scanner is another [[:Category:Modules (Utility)|passive non combat device]]. It is designed to hack into computer databases, bring down security firewalls and to give total access to sensitive information.

== Where to Acquire ==
The ComWave Scanner can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
